@orderId = YOUR_ORDER_ID_HERE

### ==================== ADMIN: QUERY ALL ORDERS ====================

### 1. Get all orders (no filter)
GET {{baseUrl}}

### 2. Get orders by status - pending
GET {{baseUrl}}?status=pending

### 3. Get orders by status - accepted
GET {{baseUrl}}?status=accepted

### 4. Get orders by status - preparing
GET {{baseUrl}}?status=preparing

### 5. Get orders by table
GET {{baseUrl}}?tableId={{tableId}}

### 6. Get orders by date
GET {{baseUrl}}?date=2025-12-31

### 7. Get orders with limit
GET {{baseUrl}}?limit=10

### 8. Get orders with multiple filters
GET {{baseUrl}}?status=pending&limit=5

### ==================== GET SPECIFIC ORDER ====================

### 9. Get active order for a table
GET {{baseUrl}}/table/{{tableId}}

### 10. Get order by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/{{orderId}}

